<h1 class="is-visually-hidden">Rancho Esperanza</h1>

<h2>Jiquilillo&rsquo;s hostel with a conscience, where you can do a lot or a little and still make a difference</h2>

<figure>
  <img src="assets/images/photo-home-beach.jpg" alt="">
  <figcaption>Our beach house, palapas and coconut thatched hammock area provide comfort from the sun while you enjoy the refreshing sea breeze.</figcaption>
</figure>

<p>Our idyllic beach front backpacker hostel combines <a href="accommodation-and-prices.html" title="Learn about the accommodation we offer">low-impact, natural living</a> with <a href="mission-and-projects.html" title="Learn about our mission and projects">projects that actively benefit the village</a>.</p>

<p>Whether you are looking to escape, contemplate and create, <a href="excursions-and-activities.html#surfing" title="Learn about our surfing services">surf</a>, or just unwind for a few days, Rancho Esperanza lets you appreciate authentic Nicaraguan life at the beautiful beach setting of <a href="about-jiquilillo.html" title="Learn about Jiquilillo">Jiquilillo</a> where you'll be confident that your presence is doing good not harm.</p>

<figure class="pull-right">
  <img src="assets/images/photo-home-nate.jpg" alt="">
  <figcaption>Nate reading from his 300+ book library inside the spacious common area of the main rancho.</figcaption>
</figure>

<p>If you want a new perspective, our <a href="volunteer-opportunities.html" title="Learn how to become a volunteer with us">volunteer opportunities</a> give you a chance to get involved in our community projects. We offer <a href="excursions-and-activities.html#surfing" title="Learn about our surfing services">surf rentals and surf lessons</a>, and also provide board repair. The local kids within <a href="mission-and-projects.html#surf-club" title="Learn about our Surf Club project">Surf Club</a> can provide their knowledge of local beach breaks, including the nearby shore and point breaks of El Asserradores.</p>

<p>For the adventurous, <a href="excursions-and-activities.html" title="Learn about our community-based tours">we and the community offer</a> kayaking, volcano hikes, horse back riding and <a href="excursions-and-activities.html#cultural-excursions" title="Learn about our cultural excursions">cultural excursions</a>.</p>

